nodes.text: The Corellian bloc was a coalition of Corellian colonies in the Trans-Nebular sector. One of the colonies was the Baylin Cluster.

They were founded some time before 4000 BBY and came into conflict with Barralenal, a group of Aqualish pilgrims who had settled in the same sector. Republic Governor Matri Bey was unable to prevent both factions from engaging in war.
